verbose_text: Further, as an extension of our previous data that showed that AG suppressed AOM / DSS induced CAC and modulated the adipogenesis related signaling pathway in HFD induced obesity mice, our study demonstrated that AG significantly suppressed the development and progression of HFD propelled CAC through modulating the STAT3 signaling pathway.
evidence: CAC and modulated the adipogenesis-related signaling pathway in HFD
